CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 18, 1947, pg. 9, reads: "Pouring Tea - Pouring tea at the Sunday tea given by the Beauty Shop Owners Association were, left: Mrs. Irene Leonard, and right, Mrs. Julia Chilton. Standing by are, left to right: Lucille Buckner, general chairman of the event; Mildred Brown, Bernice Clark, Anna Turner, Kathleen Holloway and Mayolla Jordan. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Formal tea given by Beauty Shop Owners Association with Irene Leonard seated on left, Lucille Buckner, Mildred Brown, Bernice Clark, Anna Turner, Kathleen Holloway, Mayolla Jordon, and Julia Chilton seated on right, in library
